message: Let's be fair, 60-40 is a good deal!
I appreciate the offer Alice, but I think a 52.5/47.5 split is more reflective of the time pressure and the risk of us both getting nothing.
I can do 58-42, it's as low as I'm willing to go for now.
Alice, let's stop wasting time. A 50/50 split is the fairest and ensures we both benefit. Time is running out!
